OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBlustery shower in the north
OL,6,Fwill continue this morning, with snow
OL,7,Fover the hills at first, but these
OL,8,Fwill gradually ease through the day.
OL,9,FLargely dry in the south with sunny
OL,10,Fspells, although a few showers
OL,11,Fpossible. Winds easing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FClear spells in the east at
OL,14,Ffirst with a frost developing. Skies
OL,15,Fclouding over elsewhere with outbreaks
OL,16,Fof rain and drizzle.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
