OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FCloudy at first with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain and drizzle. Turning
OL,7,Fdrier for many in the afternoon with
OL,8,Fsome warm bright or sunny spells.
OL,9,FWindy in the north with coastal gales.
